|imdb = http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0118688/}}'''Sean Buckley''' is an English actor who has appeared in films such as "The Fifth Element" and "Les Miserables".

In ''[[Game of Thrones (TV series)|Game of Thrones]]'' he portrayed the [[Old man]] in the episode "[[The Rains of Castamere (episode)|The Rains of Castamere]]". He joined the cast as a guest star in the [[Season 3|third season]].
